<p>
	This elegantly stunning and unique ceramic oil burner comes in two parts creating the yin and yang symbol when fitted together. One half of the oil burner is black and the other is white and it has a delicate Buddha and symbol design covering the outside of the burner. This oil burner is fantastic for burning two of your favourite oils at the same time or for blending and experimenting with different oils to create new fragrances. The oil burner with both pieces fitted together measures 9cm tall and 12cm in diameter.</p>
